    "content" : [ {
      "html" : "<div style=\"white-space: pre\">I'll never tire of saying this. Don't use `border`. Use `outline` instead.\n\n\"Why, Kyle?\"\n\nBecause `border` will shift layout. Those extra pixels may make something wrap that shouldn't. Whereas `outline` will not affect layout while giving you the same information for debugging.</div>",
